[{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0948","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0948.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0636","title":"多厂商 Discard 服务安全配置漏洞","description":"Discard 服务（RFC 863，TCP/UDP 端口 9）是一种诊断网络服务，收到所有数据后直接丢弃而不做任何处理。该服务在生产环境中启用会无谓增加系统攻击面，攻击者可通过端口扫描发现该服务并确认主机存活，用于网络侦察；在 UDP 模式下，还可被用于反射放大 DDoS 攻击的流量放大链，导致目标网络带宽耗尽。此外，大量向该服务发送数据包可能造成服务器资源消耗。该漏洞无需认证、可远程利用，影响所有启用了 discard 服务的系统，应关闭该服务或通过防火墙限制访问。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0636"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-01-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:46.037","remediation":"在 Linux/Unix 中编辑 /etc/inetd.conf 注释 discard 相关行（stream 和 dgram）并重启 inetd 服务；systemd 系统执行 systemctl mask discard.socket 停止并屏蔽 discard socket。Windows 系统通过控制面板取消勾选\"简单 TCP/IP 服务\"或运行 dism /online /disable-feature /featurename:SimpleTCP 卸载。同时建议在防火墙上阻断 TCP 和 UDP 端口 9 的入站流量，并检查禁用 echo（端口 7）、chargen（端口 19）等类似高危服务。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://www.cve.org/CVERecord?id=CVE-1999-0636","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/1421f0a4349d5d46275cadd9c7c62349edf9c8bb/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0636.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0636","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0636.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-0636.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/2f876a2c24d5ccd5bbd081f09e801e580536456a/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0636.json","https://github.com/xqcyberscore/nvt/blob/978f6a9acb495d7d669239530ffe6da5d631f4da/SHN_discard.nasl","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/d21eb36f6164170df89822577def7df5351966d2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-0636.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x84000/83127/info.html","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--78c74f51-06af-4c13-a78e-77284614fcad.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0948.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0946","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0946.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0635","title":"多种操作系统 Echo 服务运行反射放大拒绝服务漏洞","description":"回声服务（Echo Service）运行于 TCP/UDP 端口 7，该服务将接收到的任意数据原样返回给发送方。攻击者可利用此服务进行信息收集，探测目标系统存活状态；更严重的是，攻击者可伪造源地址利用 UDP 回声服务发起反射放大型拒绝服务攻击，大量响应数据包会涌向被伪造的目标地址，导致目标带宽或资源耗尽。该漏洞影响默认开启该服务的所有旧版本操作系统。修复建议为禁用回声服务或通过防火墙阻止外部对端口 7 的访问。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0635"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-01-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:45.917","remediation":"立即禁用回声服务（echo service）：在 Unix/Linux 系统中注释 `/etc/inetd.conf` 中的 echo 行并重启 inetd，或执行 `systemctl disable echo-dgram echo-stream` 禁用 systemd socket；在 Windows 系统中通过服务管理器停止并禁用 Simple TCP/IP Services 或使用 `sc stop echo` 命令。同时在边界防火墙上封禁 UDP/TCP 7 端口以防止反射放大攻击。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://lists.grok.org.uk/pipermail/full-disclosure/2006-January/041434.html","http://secunia.com/advisories/18514","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/34851454a7b07498072de47d56f63daa4a4f524d/1999/CVE-1999-0635.md","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/1421f0a4349d5d46275cadd9c7c62349edf9c8bb/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0635.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0635","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0635.json","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/2f876a2c24d5ccd5bbd081f09e801e580536456a/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0635.json","https://github.com/mabitoski/cve_submodules/blob/44ad7e2705b3aef1b2ffaf64bd47596c10a6c2e4/1999/CVE-1999-0635.md","https://github.com/rhuitl/uClinux/blob/0486e80a025dccbe4a2213715a2ab8a5063ea86b/user/nessus/nessus-plugins/scripts/echo.nasl","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0635.json","https://github.com/entrysky/mageni/blob/c58dcc9bc43b7fb267bb10a8083ada356fbc81d1/plugins/2009/echo_udp.nasl"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0946.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0945","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0945.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0634","title":"SSH 服务运行配置暴露","description":"CVE-1999-0634 已被拒绝使用。该编号原用于描述\"SSH 服务正在运行\"这一配置状态，但经评估该条目并非直接引入安全漏洞的缺陷，而属于安全配置管理范畴。此类配置项更适合纳入通用配置枚举（CCE）体系进行管理，因此 CVE 编号委员会决定拒绝此编号。该问题不涉及具体的攻击方法、漏洞原理或影响范围。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0634"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-01-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2023-11-07T01:54:59.870","remediation":"评估 SSH 服务是否必需，非必需则关闭 sshd 服务（systemctl disable sshd）；如需保留，配置密钥认证登录、禁用 root 直接登录（PermitRootLogin no）、修改默认端口 22 为高编号端口、限制来源 IP（hosts.allow/iptables），并保持 OpenSSH 为最新稳定版本。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/1421f0a4349d5d46275cadd9c7c62349edf9c8bb/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0634.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0634","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/2f876a2c24d5ccd5bbd081f09e801e580536456a/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0634.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0634.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/lymwhen/lymwhen.github.io/blob/b77540924df6be1e7c614e34dd724374affd2cbf/Linux/%E6%BC%8F%E6%B4%9E%E4%BF%AE%E5%A4%8D.md","https://github.com/athiasjerome/XORCISM/blob/327e2a3be196660f82c89ae9d7c4e7abe4785b0d/SOURCES/XProviderQualys/QualysSampleResults.xml","https://github.com/fkie-cad/nvd-json-data-feeds/blob/5c36feecacaa0eef96caef76eb433e2bf57c7235/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-06xx/CVE-1999-0634.json","https://github.com/thoraf20/vulnscan/blob/600477d061ab5462099630f9f0924cc5383c5452/network.csv"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0945.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0943","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0943.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0633","title":"HTTP/WWW 服务运行配置检查项（非漏洞）","description":"CVE-1999-0633 已被官方驳回（REJECT），原候选编号指向\"HTTP/WWW 服务正在运行\"这一配置检测项。该条目涉及的是系统上 HTTP 服务端口的开放状态识别，并非安全漏洞，不具备攻击条件和利用方式，不产生 CVSS 评分。此类配置检查更适合归入通用配置枚举（CCE）体系，而非 CVE 漏洞编号体系。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0633"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-01-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2023-11-07T01:54:59.750","remediation":"若 HTTP 服务非业务必需，应在系统服务管理器中禁用 httpd/nginx/IIS 等相关服务并配置防火墙阻止 80/443 端口入站流量；若为业务必要，应确保移除默认页面、禁用目录列表、限制访问来源 IP、启用 TLS 并定期更新 Web 服务器至最新稳定版本。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/1421f0a4349d5d46275cadd9c7c62349edf9c8bb/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0633.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0633","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/2f876a2c24d5ccd5bbd081f09e801e580536456a/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0633.json","https://github.com/scipag/AttackToolKit/blob/78bf88564956b8f18a37659dc3d345093e95a136/plugins/HTTP%20index.html%20check.plugin","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0633.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_000461.txt","https://github.com/lymwhen/lymwhen.github.io/blob/b77540924df6be1e7c614e34dd724374affd2cbf/Linux/%E6%BC%8F%E6%B4%9E%E4%BF%AE%E5%A4%8D.md","https://github.com/Planet-Source-Code/marc-ruef-attack-tool-kit-4-0__1-58262/blob/47bd1012c1edf591e9c9fe874122b617137e1b87/atk-4.0src/plugins/HTTP%20404%20enumeration.plugin","https://github.com/zmerry/z-marvel.github.io/blob/581a79f0e7ceb8cdb3e444922154e004cca44bbb/vulbox/webvul/low/%E5%8F%AF%E9%80%9A%E8%BF%87HTTP%E8%8E%B7%E5%8F%96%E8%BF%9C%E7%AB%AFWWW%E6%9C%8D%E5%8A%A1%E4%BF%A1%E6%81%AF.html"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0943.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0939","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0939.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0632","title":"通用 RPC Portmapper 服务信息泄露漏洞","description":"系统运行了 RPC 端口映射服务（rpcbind），该服务会向远程查询者暴露主机上运行的所有 RPC 服务的程序号、版本号和端口号。未经身份认证的远程攻击者可利用该服务收集系统上运行的 RPC 服务清单，从而获取目标系统信息以辅助进一步攻击，构成信息泄露风险。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.3,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0632"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-01-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:45.710","remediation":"在网络边界防火墙上阻止 TCP/UDP 111 端口的入站流量，防止外部枚举 RPC 服务。如业务不需要 RPC 服务，可禁用 portmap/rpcbind 服务（Linux 上执行 `systemctl disable rpcbind && systemctl stop rpcbind`）；若需使用，应限制仅信任来源 IP 可访问，避免暴露在公网。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://www.cve.org/CVERecord?id=CVE-1999-0632","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/269e5b2b6ea60fdb4a03411be38d3e381b26e4c4/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0632.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0632","https://github.com/cisagov/vulnrichment/blob/f06304a9243ce013bfbf7cea427539f6409c0a05/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0632.json","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0632.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-0632.md","https://github.com/packetchaos/navi/blob/48d4e8df93f0f87e8654f6bfb01844b5dea4ed58/Queries.md","https://github.com/rhuitl/uClinux/blob/0486e80a025dccbe4a2213715a2ab8a5063ea86b/user/nessus/nessus-plugins/scripts/rpc_portmap.nasl","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/2f876a2c24d5ccd5bbd081f09e801e580536456a/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0632.json","https://github.com/defenxor/dsiem/blob/a436146a07576ac81c0b2e02afb7b5e88114951b/internal/pkg/plugin/nesd/fixtures/nessus_example.csv","https://github.com/blackhook/nessus-plugins/blob/64177d96abbb07c58cf7e131046b067ebc61fcb5/R/rpc_portmap_port32771.nasl"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0939.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0937","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0937.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0631","title":"NFS 服务未授权访问配置问题","description":"该漏洞为已被撤销的 CVE 编号，原指 NFS（网络文件系统）服务在目标主机上处于运行状态。NFS 服务默认监听 TCP/UDP 2049 端口，若未配置严格的访问控制策略（如 exports 权限限制、IP 过滤、认证机制），远程未授权攻击者可通过网络探测到该服务，进而可能尝试挂载或访问导出的文件系统，导致敏感文件泄露或进一步渗透。该问题不属于安全漏洞范畴，已被转移至通用配置枚举（CCE）进行管理，CVSS 评分 0.0，不涉及具体的攻击利用链路或需修复的软件缺陷。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0631"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-01-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2023-11-07T01:54:59.713","remediation":"如非业务需要，应在不需要 NFS 共享的服务器上关闭 NFS 服务（systemctl disable nfs-server）；确需使用时，应限制 exports 仅允许特定 IP 段访问并使用 root_squash 选项，同时在防火墙中限制 2049/TCP 端口仅对受信来源开放，推荐启用 NFSv4 及以上版本并禁用 NFSv2/v3","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/269e5b2b6ea60fdb4a03411be38d3e381b26e4c4/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0631.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0631","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/2f876a2c24d5ccd5bbd081f09e801e580536456a/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0631.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0631.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/fkie-cad/nvd-json-data-feeds/blob/1b69cf2313f68e29acceed58f52f6109cd37bb04/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-06xx/CVE-1999-0631.json","https://github.com/williamjsmail/piranha/blob/e60f12e6edcde8585ee473f701c2421f6efe72d9/CVE2CAPEC/database/CVE-1999.jsonl","https://github.com/cmjayasinghe/Threat-Intelligence-Dashboard/blob/ccfec8014cc85c9e776b8f657bdb7879139ab5ed/data/cves.csv","https://github.com/Software-Engineering-2026-Class/kelompok4-cyber-kg-agentic/blob/0fc3a7d1e2416617ef834c956997e1f0f283424b/parser_agent/output/cve.ttl"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0937.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0932","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0932.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0629","title":"通用 ident/identd 服务信息泄露漏洞","description":"ident/identd 服务（RFC 1413）运行时会监听 113 端口，为任何 TCP 连接请求返回对应进程的拥有者用户名。未经授权的远程攻击者可利用该服务枚举系统上的用户账户信息，为后续暴力破解或针对性攻击提供侦察支持。虽然该服务本身不直接导致代码执行，但其暴露的用户信息会降低系统安全防护等级，属于信息泄露风险。建议在非必要情况下禁用该服务或通过防火墙限制对 113 端口的访问。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0629"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-01-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:45.460","remediation":"建议立即停止 identd 服务并禁用其开机自启：在 Linux 系统中执行 `systemctl stop identd && systemctl disable identd`（或 `service identd stop && chkconfig identd off`）；在 Cisco IOS 上执行 `no service tcp-small-servers`。同时通过防火墙屏蔽 TCP 端口 113，阻止外部访问该服务。如无业务依赖，应彻底卸载 identd 软件包（如 `apt-get remove identd`）。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0629","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/34851454a7b07498072de47d56f63daa4a4f524d/1999/CVE-1999-0629.md","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/ab669d9fb37e52ed0619cb2b8265d34528fbe875/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0629.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0629","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0629.json","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/2f876a2c24d5ccd5bbd081f09e801e580536456a/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0629.json","https://github.com/mabitoski/cve_submodules/blob/44ad7e2705b3aef1b2ffaf64bd47596c10a6c2e4/1999/CVE-1999-0629.md","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0629.json","https://github.com/JakeVincet/nvt/blob/f39b9cba98d614dd2a567b15cce1a5eeb97ad782/auth_enabled.nasl","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x84000/83127/info.html","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0932.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0918","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0918.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0625","title":"UNIX rpc.rquotad 远程权限提升漏洞","description":"rpc.rquotad（远程磁盘配额守护进程）是基于 RPC 协议的过时服务，默认通过端口映射器注册，允许任意远程用户无需认证即可查询目标系统的用户磁盘配额信息。攻击者可通过 RPC 扫描探测该服务，从而获取系统用户名列表及配额使用情况，为后续密码爆破或权限提升攻击收集侦察信息。该协议缺乏安全认证与加密机制，属于不安全配置问题而非软件缺陷，应当禁用。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0625"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-01-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:44.947","remediation":"建议立即禁用 rpc.rquotad 服务：在 Linux 中执行 `systemctl stop rpc-rquotad && systemctl disable rpc-rquotad`（或 `killall rpc.rquotad`）；在 /etc/inetd.conf 中注释掉 rquotad 行并重启 inetd。同时配置 iptables 防火墙规则限制对 RPC 端口 111 和 2049 的外部访问，仅允许受信 IP 段。如在共享存储场景中必需，替换为 NFSv4 内建配额管理，不再依赖独立 rquotad 服务。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://www.cve.org/CVERecord?id=CVE-1999-0625","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/297eb115816d3735806f02ee33bb4d2d53ecd5c6/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0625.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0625","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0625.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-0625.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/2ed73314b4d66512efbb22e0644e615bc00001f2/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0625.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/49899a53e9c2e620c99e0234afe3c50e512ad851/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-r8qg-5ffw-4wgf/GHSA-r8qg-5ffw-4wgf.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/blackhook/nessus-plugins/blob/64177d96abbb07c58cf7e131046b067ebc61fcb5/R/rpc_rquotad.nasl","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x84000/83127/info.html","https://github.com/fkie-cad/nvd-json-data-feeds/blob/1b69cf2313f68e29acceed58f52f6109cd37bb04/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-06xx/CVE-1999-0625.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0918.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0916","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0916.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0624","title":"Sun Microsystems RPC rstatd 服务权限提升漏洞","description":"rstatd（远程统计服务）是基于 RPC 协议运行的系统服务，默认监听在端口 111/TCP 或 111/UDP，向未经身份认证的远程攻击者提供系统性能统计数据（包括 CPU 负载、磁盘 I/O、内存使用等敏感信息）。该服务本身不提供任何访问控制机制，攻击者无需任何凭证即可通过 rpcinfo 或 rstat 协议查询目标系统，导致系统运行状态信息泄露。泄露的信息可被用于识别系统负载模式、辅助后续精准攻击。此外，常见 rstatd 实现（如 SunOS、Linux 等）历史上存在缓冲区溢出漏洞，远程攻击者可利用特制 RPC 请求触发拒绝服务甚至远程代码执行。该漏洞影响所有运行 rstatd 服务的 UNIX/Linux 系统，属于高危暴露风险。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0624"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-01-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:44.800","remediation":"禁用 rstat/rstatd 服务，执行 `chkconfig rstatd off`（SysV）或 `systemctl disable rstatd && systemctl stop rstatd`（systemd），并在防火墙中封禁端口 111 (TCP/UDP，portmapper) 和 rstatd 使用的随机 UDP 端口范围，阻止外部 RPC 查询。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://www.cve.org/CVERecord?id=CVE-1999-0624","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/34851454a7b07498072de47d56f63daa4a4f524d/1999/CVE-1999-0624.md","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/297eb115816d3735806f02ee33bb4d2d53ecd5c6/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0624.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0624","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0624.json","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/2ed73314b4d66512efbb22e0644e615bc00001f2/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0624.json","https://github.com/mabitoski/cve_submodules/blob/44ad7e2705b3aef1b2ffaf64bd47596c10a6c2e4/1999/CVE-1999-0624.md","https://github.com/xqcyberscore/nvt/blob/978f6a9acb495d7d669239530ffe6da5d631f4da/2011/secpod_rpc_rstatd_udp.nasl","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0624.json","https://github.com/LubyRuffy/plugins/blob/f873b19f27c95eaf2993ca4acde5cb7965d2ee3f/2011/secpod_rpc_rstatd_tcp.nasl","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x84000/83127/info.html"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0916.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0915","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0915.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0623","title":"X.Org X Window System 服务配置不当","description":"CVE-1999-0623 已被 NVD 官方拒绝使用，原因为该候选编号描述的是一个系统配置检查项（X Window 服务正在运行），而非直接构成安全漏洞的缺陷。此类配置检测更适合归入通用配置枚举（CCE）体系管理，不应作为漏洞编号使用。该条目无 CVSS 评分，无有效影响范围与攻击条件说明。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0623"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-01-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2023-11-07T01:54:59.640","remediation":"若无需图形界面或远程 X11 功能，建议关闭 X Window 服务（如 Linux 下执行 `systemctl stop gdm` 并禁用开机启动）。如需使用 X11 转发，应限制仅监听 127.0.0.1，并通过 SSH 隧道（`ssh -X`）安全转发，避免将 TCP 端口 6000 暴露到外部网络。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/297eb115816d3735806f02ee33bb4d2d53ecd5c6/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0623.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0623","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/2ed73314b4d66512efbb22e0644e615bc00001f2/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0623.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0623.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/fkie-cad/nvd-json-data-feeds/blob/1b69cf2313f68e29acceed58f52f6109cd37bb04/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-06xx/CVE-1999-0623.json","https://github.com/williamjsmail/piranha/blob/e60f12e6edcde8585ee473f701c2421f6efe72d9/CVE2CAPEC/database/CVE-1999.jsonl","https://github.com/cmjayasinghe/Threat-Intelligence-Dashboard/blob/ccfec8014cc85c9e776b8f657bdb7879139ab5ed/data/cves.csv","https://github.com/Software-Engineering-2026-Class/kelompok4-cyber-kg-agentic/blob/0fc3a7d1e2416617ef834c956997e1f0f283424b/parser_agent/output/cve.ttl"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0915.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0914","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0914.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0622","title":"通用 DNS 服务配置检测（非安全漏洞）","description":"CVE-1999-0622 已被正式驳回（REJECT），原候选编号描述为\"DNS 相关服务组件正在运行\"。该条目仅涉及系统配置层面的 DNS 服务开放状态，属于安全配置审计范畴而非可直接利用的安全漏洞，不存在攻击路径与利用条件。此类配置信息更适合在通用配置枚举（CCE）中覆盖，不适用作 CVE 漏洞编号。因此该 CVE 不具有实际漏洞意义，不记录 CVSS 评分。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0622"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-01-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2023-11-07T01:54:59.607","remediation":"配置 DNS 服务时应限制区域传输仅允许授权的辅助 DNS 服务器，关闭递归查询或将其限制为仅内网客户端，防止 DNS 反射放大攻击。同时部署 DNSSEC 保障数据完整性，禁止版本信息泄露，并定期审计 DNS 日志。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/297eb115816d3735806f02ee33bb4d2d53ecd5c6/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0622.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0622","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/2ed73314b4d66512efbb22e0644e615bc00001f2/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0622.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0622.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa5